('INT00000216', 'CUST00000216', '2026-02-15 02:24:56.881', 'CHAT', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00016', '432', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $66. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.5600', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000217', 'CUST00000217', '2026-02-15 02:08:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00017', '449', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.4300', 'NEGATIVE', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000218', 'CUST00000218', '2026-02-15 01:51:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00018', '466', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.5800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000219', 'CUST00000219', '2026-02-15 01:34:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00019', '483', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5900', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000220', 'CUST00000220', '2026-02-15 01:18:16.881', 'PHONE', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00020', '500', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.6000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
