('INT00000345', 'CUST00000345', '2026-02-13 14:34:56.881', 'PHONE', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00145', '945', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2000', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000346', 'CUST00000346', '2026-02-13 14:18:16.881', 'CHAT', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00146', '962', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.6600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000347', 'CUST00000347', '2026-02-13 14:01:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00147', '979', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.6700', 'NEUTRAL', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000348', 'CUST00000348', '2026-02-13 13:44:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00148', '996', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $198. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.6800', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000349', 'CUST00000349', '2026-02-13 13:28:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00149', '1013', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '-0.5100', 'NEGATIVE', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000350', 'CUST00000350', '2026-02-13 13:11:36.881', 'PHONE', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00150', '1030', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.7000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
