('INT00000388', 'CUST00000388', '2026-02-13 02:38:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00188', '1676', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.4800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000389', 'CUST00000389', '2026-02-13 02:21:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00189', '1693', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.4900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000390', 'CUST00000390', '2026-02-13 02:04:56.881', 'PHONE', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00190', '1710', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '-0.3000', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000391', 'CUST00000391', '2026-02-13 01:48:16.881', 'CHAT', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00191', '1727', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.9100', 'POSITIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000392', 'CUST00000392', '2026-02-13 01:31:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00192', '1744', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.5200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000393', 'CUST00000393', '2026-02-13 01:14:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00193', '1761', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2200', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000394', 'CUST00000394', '2026-02-13 00:58:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00194', '1778', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000395', 'CUST00000395', '2026-02-13 00:41:36.881', 'PHONE', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00195', '1795', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.5500', 'NEUTRAL', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
