('INT00000431', 'CUST00000431', '2026-02-12 14:41:36.881', 'CHAT', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00031', '727', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.3100', 'NEUTRAL', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000432', 'CUST00000432', '2026-02-12 14:24:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00032', '744', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $82. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.3200', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000433', 'CUST00000433', '2026-02-12 14:08:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00033', '761', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.4700', 'NEGATIVE', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000434', 'CUST00000434', '2026-02-12 13:51:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00034', '778', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.3400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
