('INT00000603', 'CUST00000603', '2026-02-10 14:54:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00003', '291', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.2300', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000604', 'CUST00000604', '2026-02-10 14:38:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00004', '308', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.2400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000605', 'CUST00000605', '2026-02-10 14:21:36.881', 'PHONE', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00005', '325', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.2500', 'NEUTRAL', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000606', 'CUST00000606', '2026-02-10 14:04:56.881', 'CHAT', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00006', '342', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2400', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000607', 'CUST00000607', '2026-02-10 13:48:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00007', '359', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.8700', 'POSITIVE', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000608', 'CUST00000608', '2026-02-10 13:31:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00008', '376', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.2800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000609', 'CUST00000609', '2026-02-10 13:14:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00009', '393', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '-0.3100', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000610', 'CUST00000610', '2026-02-10 12:58:16.881', 'PHONE', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00010', '410', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.3000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
