('INT00000646', 'CUST00000646', '2026-02-10 02:58:16.881', 'CHAT', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00046', '1022', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.6600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000647', 'CUST00000647', '2026-02-10 02:41:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00047', '1039', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.6700', 'NEUTRAL', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000648', 'CUST00000648', '2026-02-10 02:24:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00048', '1056', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $98. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.6800', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
