('INT00000776', 'CUST00000776', '2026-02-08 14:51:36.881', 'CHAT', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00176', '1552', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.7600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000777', 'CUST00000777', '2026-02-08 14:34:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00177', '1569', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.3800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000778', 'CUST00000778', '2026-02-08 14:18:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00178', '1586', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.7800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000779', 'CUST00000779', '2026-02-08 14:01:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00179', '1603', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.7900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
