('INT00000818', 'CUST00000818', '2026-02-08 03:11:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00018', '586', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.5800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
