('INT00000860', 'CUST00000860', '2026-02-07 15:31:36.881', 'PHONE', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00060', '1300', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.4000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000861', 'CUST00000861', '2026-02-07 15:14:56.881', 'CHAT', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00061', '1317', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.2900', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000862', 'CUST00000862', '2026-02-07 14:58:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00062', '1334', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.4200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000863', 'CUST00000863', '2026-02-07 14:41:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00063', '1351', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.4300', 'NEUTRAL', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00000864', 'CUST00000864', '2026-02-07 14:24:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00064', '1368', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $114. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.4400', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
