('INT00001030', 'CUST00001030', '2026-02-05 16:18:16.881', 'PHONE', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00030', '830', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.3000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001031', 'CUST00001031', '2026-02-05 16:01:36.881', 'CHAT', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00031', '847', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.3100', 'NEUTRAL', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001032', 'CUST00001032', '2026-02-05 15:44:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00032', '864', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $82. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.3200', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001033', 'CUST00001033', '2026-02-05 15:28:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00033', '881', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.4700', 'NEGATIVE', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
