('INT00001072', 'CUST00001072', '2026-02-05 04:38:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00072', '1544', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.7200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001073', 'CUST00001073', '2026-02-05 04:21:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00073', '1561', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.7300', 'NEUTRAL', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001074', 'CUST00001074', '2026-02-05 04:04:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00074', '1578', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '-0.0600', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001075', 'CUST00001075', '2026-02-05 03:48:16.881', 'PHONE', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00075', '1595', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.9500', 'POSITIVE', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001076', 'CUST00001076', '2026-02-05 03:31:36.881', 'CHAT', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00076', '1612', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.7600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001077', 'CUST00001077', '2026-02-05 03:14:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00077', '1629', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.3800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
