('INT00001199', 'CUST00001199', '2026-02-03 17:21:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00199', '343', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.7900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001200', 'CUST00001200', '2026-02-03 17:04:56.881', 'PHONE', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00000', '360', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $50. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.2000', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001201', 'CUST00001201', '2026-02-03 16:48:16.881', 'CHAT', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00001', '377', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.5900', 'NEGATIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
