('INT00001241', 'CUST00001241', '2026-02-03 05:41:36.881', 'CHAT', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00041', '1057', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.6100', 'NEUTRAL', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001242', 'CUST00001242', '2026-02-03 05:24:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00042', '1074', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
