('INT00001367', 'CUST00001367', '2026-02-01 18:41:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00167', '1519', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.6700', 'NEUTRAL', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001368', 'CUST00001368', '2026-02-01 18:24:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00168', '1536', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $218. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.6800', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001369', 'CUST00001369', '2026-02-01 18:08:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00169', '1553', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '-0.5100', 'NEGATIVE', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001370', 'CUST00001370', '2026-02-01 17:51:36.881', 'PHONE', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00170', '1570', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.7000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
