('INT00001409', 'CUST00001409', '2026-02-01 07:01:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00009', '553', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.4900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001410', 'CUST00001410', '2026-02-01 06:44:56.881', 'PHONE', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00010', '570', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '-0.3000', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001411', 'CUST00001411', '2026-02-01 06:28:16.881', 'CHAT', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00011', '587', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.9100', 'POSITIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001412', 'CUST00001412', '2026-02-01 06:11:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00012', '604', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.5200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001413', 'CUST00001413', '2026-02-01 05:54:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00013', '621', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2700', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
