('INT00001665', 'CUST00001665', '2026-01-29 07:54:56.881', 'PHONE', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00065', '1545', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2500', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
