('INT00001958', 'CUST00001958', '2026-01-25 22:31:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00158', '1486', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.5800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001959', 'CUST00001959', '2026-01-25 22:14:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00159', '1503', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5900', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001960', 'CUST00001960', '2026-01-25 21:58:16.881', 'PHONE', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00160', '1520', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.6000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001961', 'CUST00001961', '2026-01-25 21:41:36.881', 'CHAT', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00161', '1537', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.6100', 'NEUTRAL', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001962', 'CUST00001962', '2026-01-25 21:24:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00162', '1554', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001963', 'CUST00001963', '2026-01-25 21:08:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00163', '1571', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.8300', 'POSITIVE', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001964', 'CUST00001964', '2026-01-25 20:51:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00164', '1588', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.6400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001965', 'CUST00001965', '2026-01-25 20:34:56.881', 'PHONE', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00165', '1605', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2500', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001966', 'CUST00001966', '2026-01-25 20:18:16.881', 'CHAT', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00166', '1622', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.6600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00001967', 'CUST00001967', '2026-01-25 20:01:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00167', '1639', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.6700', 'NEUTRAL', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
