('INT00002337', 'CUST00002337', '2026-01-21 13:14:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00137', '1209', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002338', 'CUST00002338', '2026-01-21 12:58:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00138', '1226', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.7800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002339', 'CUST00002339', '2026-01-21 12:41:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00139', '1243', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.7900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
