('INT00002675', 'CUST00002675', '2026-01-17 15:21:36.881', 'PHONE', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00075', '235', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.5500', 'NEUTRAL', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002676', 'CUST00002676', '2026-01-17 15:04:56.881', 'CHAT', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00076', '252', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $126. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.5600', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002677', 'CUST00002677', '2026-01-17 14:48:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00077', '269', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.4300', 'NEGATIVE', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
