('INT00002969', 'CUST00002969', '2026-01-14 05:41:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00169', '193', 'Customer: Your mobile app keeps crashing when I try to deposit checks. Agent: I apologize for the technical difficulties. Can you tell me what device youre using? Customer: iPhone 14. Agent: There is a known issue we are working to fix. In the meantime, I can process a temporary workaround. Would you like me to walk you through it?', 'Troubleshot mobile app check deposit issue, provided workaround', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.4900', 'NEUTRAL', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002970', 'CUST00002970', '2026-01-14 05:24:56.881', 'PHONE', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00170', '210', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '-0.3000', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002971', 'CUST00002971', '2026-01-14 05:08:16.881', 'CHAT', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00171', '227', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.9100', 'POSITIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002972', 'CUST00002972', '2026-01-14 04:51:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00172', '244', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.5200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002973', 'CUST00002973', '2026-01-14 04:34:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00173', '261', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1700', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002974', 'CUST00002974', '2026-01-14 04:18:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00174', '278', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002975', 'CUST00002975', '2026-01-14 04:01:36.881', 'PHONE', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00175', '295', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.5500', 'NEUTRAL', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002976', 'CUST00002976', '2026-01-14 03:44:56.881', 'CHAT', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00176', '312', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $226. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.5600', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00002977', 'CUST00002977', '2026-01-14 03:28:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00177', '329', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.4300', 'NEGATIVE', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
