('INT00003138', 'CUST00003138', '2026-01-12 06:44:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00138', '1386', 'Customer: I want to close my account. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. May I ask what prompted this decision? Customer: Ive found better rates elsewhere. Agent: I understand. Before you go, I wanted to let you know about our loyalty program that offers competitive rates. Would you be interested in hearing more? Customer: Okay, tell me about it.', 'Retention conversation for account closure, presented loyalty program', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1200', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00003139', 'CUST00003139', '2026-01-12 06:28:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00139', '1403', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.9900', 'POSITIVE', '4', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00003140', 'CUST00003140', '2026-01-12 06:11:36.881', 'PHONE', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00140', '1420', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.4000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00003141', 'CUST00003141', '2026-01-12 05:54:56.881', 'CHAT', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00141', '1437', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.2400', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
