('INT00003180', 'CUST00003180', '2026-01-11 19:04:56.881', 'PHONE', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00180', '420', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $230. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.2000', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00003181', 'CUST00003181', '2026-01-11 18:48:16.881', 'CHAT', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00181', '437', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.5900', 'NEGATIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
