('INT00003897', 'CUST00003897', '2026-01-03 11:54:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00097', '849', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1800', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
