('INT00004021', 'CUST00004021', '2026-01-02 01:28:16.881', 'CHAT', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00021', '1277', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.5900', 'NEGATIVE', '8', FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004022', 'CUST00004022', '2026-01-02 01:11:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00022', '1294', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.2200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
