('INT00004063', 'CUST00004063', '2026-01-01 13:48:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00063', '311', 'Customer: Thank you for the excellent service last week. Your representative Sarah was incredibly helpful. Agent: Thank you so much for taking the time to share that feedback! I will make sure Sarah and her manager know about your kind words. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?', 'Positive feedback received for representative Sarah', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.8300', 'POSITIVE', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004064', 'CUST00004064', '2026-01-01 13:31:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00064', '328', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.6400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004065', 'CUST00004065', '2026-01-01 13:14:56.881', 'PHONE', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00065', '345', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2500', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004066', 'CUST00004066', '2026-01-01 12:58:16.881', 'CHAT', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00066', '362', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.6600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004067', 'CUST00004067', '2026-01-01 12:41:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00067', '379', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.6700', 'NEUTRAL', '10', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
