('INT00004105', 'CUST00004105', '2026-01-01 02:08:16.881', 'PHONE', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00105', '1025', 'Customer: Im very frustrated with your service. This is the third time Ive called about the same issue with my online banking. Agent: I sincerely apologize for the inconvenience. Let me escalate this to our technical team right away. Customer: I just want it fixed. Agent: I completely understand. Ive created a priority ticket and you will receive a call back within 2 hours.', 'Escalated recurring technical issue with online banking to priority support', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '-0.5500', 'NEGATIVE', '6', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004106', 'CUST00004106', '2026-01-01 01:51:36.881', 'CHAT', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00106', '1042', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.4600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004107', 'CUST00004107', '2026-01-01 01:34:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00107', '1059', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '0.4700', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004108', 'CUST00004108', '2026-01-01 01:18:16.881', 'BRANCH', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00108', '1076', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.4800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
