('INT00004149', 'CUST00004149', '2025-12-31 13:54:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00149', '1773', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '-0.1600', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
