('INT00004190', 'CUST00004190', '2025-12-31 02:31:36.881', 'PHONE', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00190', '790', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.7000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004191', 'CUST00004191', '2025-12-31 02:14:56.881', 'CHAT', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00191', '807', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '0.7100', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
