('INT00004232', 'CUST00004232', '2025-12-30 14:51:36.881', 'EMAIL', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00032', '1504', 'Customer: I need help setting up automatic bill payments. Agent: Id be happy to help you set that up. Which bills would you like to automate? Customer: My utilities and car payment. Agent: Perfect. Let me walk you through the process step by step. First, lets start with your utility company.', 'Set up automatic bill payments for utilities and car payment', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.5200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004233', 'CUST00004233', '2025-12-30 14:34:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00033', '1521', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '-0.3200', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004234', 'CUST00004234', '2025-12-30 14:18:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00034', '1538', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
