('INT00004274', 'CUST00004274', '2025-12-30 03:11:36.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00074', '538', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.3400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004275', 'CUST00004275', '2025-12-30 02:54:56.881', 'PHONE', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00075', '555', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'DIGITAL_BANKING', 'RESOLVED', '0.3500', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004276', 'CUST00004276', '2025-12-30 02:38:16.881', 'CHAT', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00076', '572', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'ACCOUNT_CLOSURE', 'RESOLVED', '0.3600', 'NEUTRAL', '3', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
