('INT00004317', 'CUST00004317', '2025-12-29 15:14:56.881', 'EMAIL', 'PRODUCT_INQUIRY', 'AGT00117', '1269', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'FEEDBACK', 'RESOLVED', '-0.2300', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
