('INT00004358', 'CUST00004358', '2025-12-29 03:51:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'FEEDBACK', 'AGT00158', '286', 'Customer: I want to increase my credit limit. Agent: Id be happy to help with that. Based on your account history, you may qualify for an increase. Let me check your eligibility. Customer: That would be great. Agent: Good news! You qualify for a $5,000 increase. Would you like me to process that? Customer: Yes, thank you so much!', 'Approved credit limit increase of $5,000 based on account eligibility', 'PAYMENTS', 'RESOLVED', '0.5800', 'NEUTRAL', '7', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004359', 'CUST00004359', '2025-12-29 03:34:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'GENERAL', 'AGT00159', '303', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'FEES', 'RESOLVED', '0.5900', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004360', 'CUST00004360', '2025-12-29 03:18:16.881', 'PHONE', 'INQUIRY', 'AGT00160', '320', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'FRAUD_DISPUTE', 'PENDING', '0.6000', 'NEUTRAL', '1', FALSE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
