('INT00004401', 'CUST00004401', '2025-12-28 15:54:56.881', 'CHAT', 'COMPLAINT', 'AGT00001', '1017', 'Customer: Why was I charged an overdraft fee? I had money in my account! Agent: I understand your frustration. Let me review your account. I see that a large debit posted before your deposit cleared. Customer: That seems unfair. Agent: I agree this situation is frustrating. As a one-time courtesy, I can waive this fee for you. Customer: Thank you, I appreciate that.', 'Waived overdraft fee as one-time courtesy after explanation', 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT', 'ESCALATED', '-0.3900', 'NEGATIVE', NULL, FALSE, TRUE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004402', 'CUST00004402', '2025-12-28 15:38:16.881', 'EMAIL', 'SUPPORT', 'AGT00002', '1034', 'Customer: Im interested in opening a savings account for my child. Agent: Thats wonderful! We have several youth savings options with great benefits. The Junior Saver account has no monthly fees and earns competitive interest. Customer: That sounds perfect. What do I need to open it? Agent: Just bring your childs birth certificate and social security card to any branch.', 'Provided information on youth savings account options', 'CREDIT_REQUEST', 'RESOLVED', '0.4200', 'NEUTRAL', '5', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004403', 'CUST00004403', '2025-12-28 15:21:36.881', 'BRANCH', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00003', '1051', 'Customer: I have a question about wire transfers. Agent: Of course, I can help with that. Are you sending domestically or internationally? Customer: International to Canada. Agent: For international wires, we need the recipients bank SWIFT code and IBAN. The fee is $45 and typically arrives within 1-2 business days. Would you like to proceed?', 'Explained international wire transfer process and fees', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.4300', 'NEUTRAL', '2', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004404', 'CUST00004404', '2025-12-28 15:04:56.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00004', '1068', 'Customer: Hi, I noticed a charge on my account that I dont recognize for $54. Agent: I understand your concern. Let me look into that for you. I can see the charge was from a subscription service. Would you like me to help you dispute this? Customer: Yes please, I never signed up for that. Agent: Ive initiated a dispute and temporary credit. You should see it within 24 hours.', 'Customer disputed unrecognized charge, dispute initiated with temporary credit', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.4400', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
