('INT00004443', 'CUST00004443', '2025-12-28 04:14:56.881', 'BRANCH', 'TRANSACTION_DISPUTE', 'AGT00043', '1731', 'Customer: Can you help me understand my mortgage options? Agent: Absolutely! Based on current rates, we have several programs available. Are you looking to purchase or refinance? Customer: Refinance my current home. Agent: With your credit profile, you could potentially save around $300 per month. Would you like me to connect you with our mortgage specialist?', 'Discussed mortgage refinance options, referred to mortgage specialist', 'LOAN_INQUIRY', 'RESOLVED', '0.2300', 'NEUTRAL', NULL, TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
('INT00004444', 'CUST00004444', '2025-12-28 03:58:16.881', 'MOBILE_APP', 'ACCOUNT_CHANGE', 'AGT00044', '1748', 'Customer: I need to report my card stolen. Agent: Im sorry to hear that. Let me immediately block your current card and issue a replacement. Have you noticed any unauthorized transactions? Customer: Not yet but I want to be safe. Agent: Smart thinking. Your new card will arrive in 3-5 business days. Is there anything else I can help with?', 'Reported stolen card, blocked immediately and ordered replacement', 'CARD_SERVICES', 'RESOLVED', '0.2400', 'NEUTRAL', '9', TRUE, FALSE, '2026-02-17 14:24:56.881'),
